Description: QBAirbase is a multidimensional provenance-augmented version of the Airbase dataset. AirBase is the European air quality dataset maintained by the EEA (Environmental European Agency). The dataset is publicly available on the Web- and contains air quality monitoring data for 40 European countries. QBOAirbase represents air pollution information as an RDF data cube- which has been linked to the YAGO and DBpedia knowledge bases. QBOAirbase is based on the version 8 of the Airbase dataset.
